{"tid":1439304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行口號推薦: 港共政府，罪魁禍首","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:52:58.000Z","uid":83404,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81764e82a375c274c822f05d488572ed911243f0","tid":1439304,"uid":83404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"眼見呢幾次遊行，有好多口號都係&quot;香港人，加油&quot;<br />\n五大訴求少咗人叫，而林鄭政權近日仲拉攏政商界，打算打經濟牌威嚇兼且將經濟下滑原因嫁禍香港示威者<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，希望可以加多個口號係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共政府，<br />\n罪魁禍首。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果多人叫，同時又俾記者影到，希望可以帶返個重點到政府身上，係佢地唔聽和平示威者民意，先至搞到香港人要行動升級，同時文宣可以整多啲經濟資訊，澄清返經濟下滑嘅原因，我見係有中老年人主動停低睇連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n俾啲意見，多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c883ff782060772346cc0e7885cc398886b6e7e1","tid":1439304,"uid":83404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"十連開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3373569e48011454fad1b567d737650959059340","tid":1439304,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"擁護一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451406d08beeee0d607b46b0f553ae437695af97","tid":1439304,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"港共政府，<br />\n罪魁禍首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a4d51153a40acbd6497567e74320d320ca4d09","tid":1439304,"uid":83404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3373569e48011454fad1b567d737650959059340","tid":1439304,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"擁護一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:19:02.000Z","